				<title>星巴克韩国停业上历史课：一场品牌危机公关，给咖啡连锁本土化敲响了什么警钟？</title>
				<link>https://www.coffeeprism.com/posts/xing-ba-ke-han-guo-ting-ye-shang-li-shi-ke-yi-chan/</link>
